{
  "stem": "27150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we were in a mood that-- that the English and the-- and the French are just going back knocking Hitler.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we will come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, nothing came through, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That makes 28 days of invasion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And halfway through, the Russians came from the east because they had an agreement to divide Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I that it-- it was on the 28th of September, you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me say the president of the-- of town, the-- you see, he surrendered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Germans came two days later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In between, they came, you see, the robbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were, you see, robbing the shops and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poles, Jews, everybody-- hooligans, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were running with sort of push trolleys, you see, you know, and selling.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, and you could buy in the street whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody was, you see, happy to buy from the robbers something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the telephones there were still working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you see, that my big brother, the-- the rich one, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told him that somebody wants to sell a-- a case of sardines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because everybody wanted, you see, over the occupation to have something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, what kind of brand?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is it [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Luis Cano? ?] I told him, you old, stupid bastard you're going to buy French-- French sardines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and ordinary sardines, I-- I've not gotten-- you got used to it with-- with your father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're not a sort of a-- that people here are crazy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, you see, we stayed back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we still, you see, by that time, the-- what's it called?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Where it's no-- or when armor-- army leaves and the other comes, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There is the robbery time et cetera.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
